    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All 7 assessed credibility factors meet or exceed their required levels at MRL 2. Six factors are appropriately scoped out per the MRL 2 assessment matrix for a Class II device with medium model influence and high decision consequence. The CFD model demonstrates sufficient credibility to support the regulatory decision regarding worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the CPB device. The relative hemolysis index predictions satisfy RH < 1 across all evaluated operating conditions.",
